        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "The men looked grave, as if they suppressed opinion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000067_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000067_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "The strait she was in through pride and shrewishness could not be disguised longer: she burst out crying bitterly; they all saw it; and she attempted no further concealment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000068_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000068_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Why not ask him softer like?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000068_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000068_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Gable is a true man in that way.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000069_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000069_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"And he drives me to do what I wouldn't; yes, he does!--Tall, come indoors.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000071_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000071_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"DO NOT DESERT ME, GABRIEL!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000072_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000072_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "The note was despatched as the message had been, and Bathsheba waited indoors for the result.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "She went out when the horse was heard, and looked up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000075_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000075_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Gabriel looked at her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000078_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000078_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "She knew from the look which sentence in her note had brought him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000078_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000078_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Bathsheba followed to the field.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000079_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000079_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Gabriel was already among the turgid, prostrate forms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "It has been said that mere ease after torment is delight for a time; and the countenances of these poor creatures expressed it now. Forty nine operations were successfully performed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000080_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000080_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Four had died; three recovered without an operation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138289_000082_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138289/1460_138289_000082_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Gabriel, will you stay on with me?\" she said, smiling winningly, and not troubling to bring her lips quite together again at the end, because there was going to be another smile soon.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Every green was young, every pore was open, and every stalk was swollen with racing currents of juice. God was palpably present in the country, and the devil had gone with the world to town.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Standing before this abraded pile, the eye regarded its present usage, the mind dwelt upon its past history, with a satisfied sense of functional continuity throughout-a feeling almost of gratitude, and quite of pride, at the permanence of the idea which had heaped it up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Five decades hardly modified the cut of a gaiter, the embroidery of a smock frock, by the breadth of a hair. Ten generations failed to alter the turn of a single phrase.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "In these Wessex nooks the busy outsider's ancient times are only old; his old times are still new; his present is futurity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "So the chatter was all on her side.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Cain Ball!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Yes, Mister Oak; here I be!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Cainy now runs forward with the tar pot.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Boldwood always carried with him a social atmosphere of his own, which everybody felt who came near him; and the talk, which Bathsheba's presence had somewhat suppressed, was now totally suspended.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "What they conversed about was not audible to Gabriel, who was too independent to get near, though too concerned to disregard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Concerning the flock?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Apparently not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000028_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000028_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Gabriel theorized, not without truth, that in quiet discussion of any matter within reach of the speakers' eyes, these are usually fixed upon it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "The animal plunged; Bathsheba instantly gazed towards it, and saw the blood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Bottle!\" he shouted, in an unmoved voice of routine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Take my place in the barn, Gabriel, and keep the men carefully to their work.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "The horses' heads were put about, and they trotted away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"Well, better wed over the mixen than over the moor,\" said Laban Tall, turning his sheep.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"So I said, 'Mistress Everdene, there's places empty, and there's gifted men willing; but the spite'--no, not the spite-I didn't say spite-'but the villainy of the contrarikind,' I said (meaning womankind), 'keeps 'em out.' That wasn't too strong for her, say?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
