        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "\"'Ithout doubt you was-'ithout doubt.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000064_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000064_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "He did not covet the post relatively to the farm: in relation to herself, as beloved by him and unmarried to another, he had coveted it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000064_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000064_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "His lecture to her was, he thought, one of the absurdest mistakes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1460_138290_000064_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1460/138290/1460_138290_000064_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1460",
        "content": "Far from coquetting with Boldwood, she had trifled with himself in thus feigning that she had trifled with another.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
